## ğŸ¯ When to Use Zustand vs React Query

### âœ… Use Zustand for:
- Client-side state (UI state, user preferences)
- Auth tokens
- App settings
- Temporary data (form state, UI flags)

### âœ… Use React Query for:
- Server state (API data)
- Cached data
- Data fetching
- Data mutations

